      <hedline>
        <hl1>Patrick Sings Merengue And Offers Inspiration</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Saul D Raw letter lauds July 30 article on Irish-American merengue star named Patrick (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Your article ''The Name's Patrick, and He's a Merengue Star'' (Citypeople, July 30) was uplifting. It shows that one can really do just about anything in this world. As a bilingual person who is now learning a third language (Spanish), I have a distant dream that maybe there will be some new career waiting for me down the road.</p>
        <p>SAUL D. RAW  Park Slope, Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
